Puppet module: motd

# Written by Tom McGonagle #
# mcgonagle@gmail.com
# Google Voice (617)229-5185
# http://www.puppetll.com


DESCRIPTION:
This module installs and manages motd software
Standard and extended classes are available.
Decide and customize how you want to define configation files: static files, templates, infile modifications...


USAGE:
# Standard Classes 
include motd              # Install and run motd with standard configurations.
include motd::disable     # Disable motd service.
include motd::disableboot # Disable motd service at boot time, but don't stop if it's running.
include motd::absent      # Remove motd package.

DEPENDENCIES:
